<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 11 at 7:36AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Snow increases as you approach Monida Pass...
At 730 AM, moderate snowfall is falling near Monida Pass. The
snowfall intensity increases as you continue southward into Idaho,
where a winter storm warning is in effect.
For those traveling south on I-15 from Lima to Monida Pass, or on
Highway 87 over Raynolds Pass, be prepared for changing road
conditions and areas of reduced visibility.</description>
